---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Bobby Ma • Cybersecurity Portfolio"
  description="Cybersecurity student portfolio: projects, labs, and technical writing."
>
  <section class="intro">
    <h1>Bobby Ma</h1>
    <p class="lead">
      Cybersecurity student building practical projects, documenting what I learn,
      and turning a home lab into a real engineering playground.
    </p>
    <p class="sub">
      Interests: blue-team foundations, detection & response, Linux hardening, and
      building tooling that makes security measurable.
    </p>
  </section>

  <div class="status-box">
    <h3>Current Status</h3>
    <p>
      Building my portfolio + blog • Running an Ubuntu home server with monitoring
      + Discord alerts • Preparing to publish hands-on lab writeups
    </p>
  </div>

  <section class="focus-areas">
    <h2>What I’m focusing on</h2>
    <div class="grid">
      <div class="focus-card">
        <h3>Linux & Infrastructure</h3>
        <p>Hardening servers, service monitoring, backups, and clean deployments.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="focus-card">
        <h3>Detection Thinking</h3>
        <p>Learning how to translate attacker behavior into telemetry and rules.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="focus-card">
        <h3>Security Labs</h3>
        <p>Building repeatable exercises and documenting the results clearly.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="focus-card">
        <h3>Writing</h3>
        <p>Short, practical posts that explain what I built, broke, and fixed.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="quick-links">
    <h2>Explore</h2>
    <div class="link-grid">
      <a href="/projects" class="link-card">
        <h3>Projects</h3>
        <p>Things I’ve built and shipped</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/labs" class="link-card">
        <h3>Labs</h3>
        <p>Hands-on exercises (writeups first)</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/blog" class="link-card">
        <h3>Blog</h3>
        <p>Notes, guides, and progress logs</p>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .intro {
    margin-bottom: calc(var(--spacing-unit) * 6);
  }

  .lead {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: var(--color-text);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: calc(var(--spacing-unit) * 2);
  }

  .sub {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: calc(var(--spacing-unit) * 3);
    margin-top: calc(var(--spacing-unit) * 3);
  }

  .focus-card {
    background: var(--color-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: calc(var(--spacing-unit) * 3);
  }

  .focus-card h3 {
    margin-top: 0;
    margin-bottom: calc(var(--spacing-unit) * 2);
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-text-heading);
  }

  .focus-card p {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  .link-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: calc(var(--spacing-unit) * 3);
    margin-top: calc(var(--spacing-unit) * 3);
  }

  .link-card {
    background: var(--color-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: calc(var(--spacing-unit) * 3);
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }

  .link-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-accent);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .link-card h3 {
    margin-top: 0;
    margin-bottom: calc(var(--spacing-unit) * 1);
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: var(--color-text-heading);
  }

  .link-card p {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }
</style>
